  <h2>Plan Validation checklist</h2>
  <ul class="checklist">
    <li>Plan Brief reviewed after a break, not immediately after writing it</li>
    <li>All three validation questions answered in writing</li>
    <li>Audience is specific — not "users" or "everyone"</li>
    <li>Success criteria are measurable and falsifiable</li>
    <li>Plan has been handed to someone else (or AI) to test clarity</li>
    <li>All gaps found have been addressed in the Plan Brief</li>
    <li>Plan Brief is more specific after this pass than before it</li>
    <li>Decision to proceed to Build (or run another pass) is explicit</li>
  </ul>

